lead_paragraph: Jamal Murray had 21 points and No. 1 Kentucky scored the final 15 points of the first half on the way to beating South Florida, 84-63, in the Hoop-Hall Miami Invitational.

headline.main: Kentucky Cruises to a Win in Miami
